-Sim.

1090
01:41:42,208 --> 01:41:43,041
Vão.

1091
01:41:43,916 --> 01:41:44,916
Vão!

1092
01:41:51,416 --> 01:41:52,708
Cara, mandou ver.

1093
01:43:41,583 --> 01:43:43,041
Claro que estou com saudade.

1094
01:43:46,125 --> 01:43:48,500
